summary: An ordinance relating to the condemnation proceedings to acquire land and other property in Blocks 6 & 7, Terry's 5th Addition, Blocks 4 & 9, Plummer's Addition, and Block 213, Seattle Tidelands for the expansion of the existing city shop and storage facility under Ordinance 91851; accepting a condemnation award for Parcel 11 and authorizing the Superintendent of Buildings to enter into a lease in connection with said award.
